            "collapsible_title": "SHIPPING & RETURNS",
            "collapsible_content": "<p><strong>UK Delivery</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Standard Delivery</strong> — Free (2–3 working days).</li><li><strong>Next Day Delivery -</strong> Free (orders over £150)</li><li><strong>Next Day Delivery</strong> — £4.95</li></ul><p>Orders must be placed by 3pm (Monday–Friday, excluding Bank Holidays) to qualify for Next Day Delivery. Orders placed after 3pm or on weekends/bank holidays are processed the next working day.</p><p><strong>Returns & Exchanges</strong></p><ul><li>We accept returns within 14 days of delivery. Items must be in their original condition with all tags attached.</li><li>UK returns are subject to a £3 return fee.</li><li>Exchanges are available for sizing issues or faulty items only, free of charge.</li><li>International returns must be shipped at the customer’s expense.</li></ul><p><strong>International Delivery</strong></p><ul><li>We offer worldwide shipping with two options depending on destination:</li></ul><p><strong>DAP (Delivered At Place):</strong> Duties and taxes are payable by the customer upon arrival. Our delivery partner will contact you to arrange payment before releasing the goods.</p><p><strong>DDP (Delivered Duty Paid):</strong> Duties and taxes are included in the shipping price at checkout. No further payment is required on delivery.<br/>‌</p><ul><li>Delivery timeframes are estimated at checkout and may vary depending on customs processing times and local courier services.</li><li>We are unable to ship to certain destinations (see our full Delivery Terms & Conditions for exclusions).</li></ul>"
